<h2>Workshop Reminder: [% workshop_title %]</h2>

<p>Hello [% name || 'Participant' %],</p>

<p>This is a friendly reminder about the upcoming workshop you're registered for:</p>

<div style="background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 15px; margin: 10px 0; border-left: 4px solid #28a745;">
    <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">[% workshop_title %]</h3>
    <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0;">
        <li><strong>Instructor:</strong> [% workshop_instructor %]</li>
        <li><strong>Date:</strong> [% workshop_date %]</li>
        <li><strong>Time:</strong> [% workshop_time %][% IF workshop_end_time %] - [% workshop_end_time %][% END %]</li>
        <li><strong>Location:</strong> [% workshop_location %]</li>
    </ul>
</div>

[% IF days_until %]
<div style="background-color: #fff3cd; padding: 15px; margin: 10px 0; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;">
    <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 18px;"><strong>⏰ Starting in [% days_until %] day[% IF days_until != 1 %]s[% END %]!</strong></p>
</div>
[% END %]

<p><strong>Important reminders:</strong></p>
<ul>
    <li>Please arrive 10 minutes early to allow time for setup</li>
    <li>Bring any required materials or equipment</li>
    <li>Workshop materials are available in the workshop portal</li>
</ul>

<p>To view workshop details and materials, please visit:</p>
<p><a href="[% workshop_url %]">[% workshop_url %]</a></p>

<p>We look forward to seeing you at the workshop!</p>

<p>If you need to cancel your registration, please contact us as soon as possible.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>
The Workshop Team</p>
